    "story": {
      "title": "The Inquiry of the Sages",
      "arc": "The prologue of the Bhagavata Purana, setting the scene where Shaunaka and other sages ask Suta Gosvami six key questions about the ultimate good, the avatars of the Lord, and where Dharma has gone after Krishna's departure.",
